-- 
-- Fri Mar 14, 2014 03:14AM EDT
-- None



March 14 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several European companies, including Lufthansa and Heidelbergcement, on Friday.

HIGHLIGHTS * Construction: Berenberg downgrades Lafarge <LAFP.PA>, others [ID:nWNAB04EU3] * BASF <BASFn.DE>: JP Morgan raises target to 61 euros from 56 euros; rating underweight * Lufthansa <LHAG.DE>: Raymond James raises target to 21.50 euros from 13 euros; outperformFollowing is a summary of research actions on European companies reported by Reuters on Friday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order. See bottom of the table for sector changes.* Allianz SE <ALVG.DE>: JP Morgan raises target to 152 euros from 150 euros; overweight * Basf SE <BASFn.DE>: JP Morgan raises target to 61 euros from 56 euros; rating underweight * Buzzi Unicem <BZU.MI>: Berenberg cuts target price to 10.40 euros from 12.30 euros; sell  * Davide Campari <CPRI.MI>: Barclays cuts target to 5.25 euros from 5.60 euros; underweight * G4S PLC <GFS.L>: Jefferies cuts price target to 280p from 290p; rating buy * Heidelbergcement <HEIG.DE>: Berenberg cuts to hold from buy  * Heidelbergcement <HEIG.DE>: Berenberg raises target price to 67 euros from 63 euros  * Holcim Ltd <HOLN.VX>: Berenberg cuts to hold from buy  * Home Retail Group <HOME.L>: Barclays raises target to 150p from 140p; rating underweight * Hornbach Baumarkt <HBMG.DE>: Berenberg starts with buy; price target 40.50 euros * Hornbach Holding <HBHG_p.DE>: Berenberg starts with buy; price target 79 euros  * Hutchison China <HCM.L>: UBS cuts to neutral from buy; raises target to 1000p from 820p * Italcementi <ITAI.MI>: Berenberg cuts to sell from hold  * Italcementi <ITAI.MI>: Berenberg raises target price to 6.10 euros from 4.20 euros  * Lafarge Sa <LAFP.PA>: Berenberg cuts to sell from hold  * Lafarge Sa <LAFP.PA>: Berenberg cuts target price to 48 euros from 51 euros  * Lufthansa <LHAG.DE>: Raymond James raises target to 21.50 euros from 13 euros; outperform * Mears Group <MERG.L>: Jefferies raises price target to 485p from 435p; rating hold * Philips <PHG.AS>: Berenberg cuts price target to 28.40 euros from 31.80 euros; rating buy * Safran <SAF.PA>: JP Morgan cuts price target to 56 euros from 62 euros; rating overweight